  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX spot at 7020.72 sitting right between the massive +30.3B gamma wall at 7025 and the +13.4B wall at 7000, dealers are positioned to aggressively sell any push above 7025 and buy dips toward 7000, creating a tight trading range. The PIN regime with 157.9B total GEX suggests strong mean-reverting forces, while the recent wall_break event indicates we've likely just tested one of these key levels. Watch for rejection at 7025-7030 zone where dealers will unload delta, and support buying if we drift back toward 7000.\n\n**Bottom line:** Expect price to get pinned between 7000-7025 with limited upside beyond 7030.",
